dwm - dynamic window manager
============================
dwm is an extremely fast, small, and dynamic window manager for X.
A customized version of dwm that has these patches applied:

    - xft
	- bstack
	- grid
	- movestack
	- pertag
	- statuscolors
	- tag client counts
	- urgentborder


Installation
============

Basically make clean install, you need to edit config.mk to suit your system though.


Customization
=============

Can be done by editing either config.h or dwm.c and recompile